    Vueper Slides is an easy to use responsive & touch-ready slideshow made for VueJS.
    #[br] Inspired by #[a(href="http://kenwheeler.github.io/slick/" target="_blank") Slick].

  v-layout.max-widthed(row align-center)
    p.
      Vueper Slides comes with a minimum of styling (using the #[i BEM] convention).#[br]
      You can easily override it, the aim is to let users have their own styles.
